# BCC Fe (ferromagnet) — collinear magmom test fixture.
# Trailing 5th column is the scalar magnetic moment in μB. The XSF spec
# nominally calls this slot "atomic force"; we treat a uniform single
# trailing column as collinear magmom (promoted to [0,0,m]).
CRYSTAL
PRIMVEC
   2.866000   0.000000   0.000000
   0.000000   2.866000   0.000000
   0.000000   0.000000   2.866000
PRIMCOORD
2 1
Fe   0.000000   0.000000   0.000000   2.20
Fe   1.433000   1.433000   1.433000   2.20
